    <條號>Article 35</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[(deleted).
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 36</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[(deleted).
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 37</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The enforcement rules for the collection of vehicle license tax shall be prescribed by the municipal and county (city) governments according to this Law, and put on record with the Ministry of Finance.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <編章節>   Chapter  7  Supplemental Provisions</編章節>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 38</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This law shall be in force from the date of promulgation. However, Article 7, amended on May 30, 2014 and attached table 5 of Article 6 amended on November 14, 2016 shall take effect on January 1 of the year following the publication date on which the amendment came into effect.
]]></條文內容>
